Second Department,

February, 1960

(February 23, 1960) In the Matter of John P. Hassan, Appellant, against Magistrates’ Court of The City of New York et al., Respondents.

Motion (1) to dismiss respondents’ motion for dismissal of the appeal, (2) for reargument of motion to dispense with printing and (3) for assignment of counsel, or for other relief. Motion denied. Motion to dismiss appeal granted, without costs, and appeal dismissed. Present — Nolan, P. J., Ughetta, Kleinfeld, Pette and Brennan, JJ.
